Only the very first line of every file in this directory is considered by
evdaemon.

key - Bit values of keys evdaemon should filter. Defined using the same syntax
      as keys displayed in /proc/bus/input/devices, i.e. at most 16 hex values
      per block, at most 12 blocks, most significant bit first.
rel - Bit values of relative axis evdaemon should filter. Defines using the same
      syntax as relative axis displayed in /proc/bus/input/devices, i.e. at
      most 16 hex values per block, at most 1 block, most significant bit first.
